snippet.title: Diana's Glam Day Out at the Mermaids of Arabia
snippet.description:
Diana and her Friends visited the magical boutique Mermaids of Arabia, Dubai Mall. The Sea Fairies turned Diana and her friends into Mermaid Princesses. The girls watched a mesmerizing Mermaid show inside Aquarium and had a princess photo shoot. It was an unforgettable glamorous day!
